item.title: dream flew on UFO
item.description: 16:41 Monday 16 April 2018 JST Had a very interesting dream last night. Most of the following was transcribed in a text message to Christine while walking to the station. I was out on a field and we saw a spaceship flying above the clouds; it was moving to and fro, and had large glowing green and red lights illuminating large portions of the clouds around it.
